parameters:
Mel: ...So, what you're saying is that
this girl named Shemini had fallen in
love with Claudia and it caused quite a
commotion.

Claudia: Yes, I did receive the resin
gemstone as a gift though.

Zerachiel: Have we gathered all the
materials for the curse-breaking potion?

Mel: Yes, it seems like we can somehow
produce it with this.

Mel: It should be completed by tomorrow
morning.

Zerachiel: Mel, thank you for helping me
even though it was a sudden request.

Zerachiel: I couldn't have made it on my
own.

Zerachiel: I wonder how I should thank
everyone...

Sachia: Ahaha, you don't have to worry
about it.
Rabi: Yes, I had a great time!

Mel: We should help each other when
we're in trouble.

Mel: If it's a request from my older
sister, I can't refuse.

Zerachiel: ...Nee-sama? What are you
talking about?
Mel: U-um, did you perhaps not know?

Mel: Aries is my older sister. We may
not be blood-related, though.

Zerachiel: No way... That's why you're
so knowledgeable about the Demon
Continent...

Zerachiel: It was thanks to Aries that
she introduced me to Unie...

Mel: If you meet her over there, please
tell her about me.

Mel: Let's have a drink together
sometime.

Zerachiel: Understood, I will definitely
convey it.
Zerachiel: Thank you all so much!!

Sachia: Ahaha, let's wait to say thank
you until we've successfully completed
it.

Claudia: I intend to not fail in the
production of the curse-breaking potion,
but...

Claudia: However, whether the curse will
be successfully broken or not depends on
luck.

Rabi: Don't worry, Zerachiel. I believe
we will succeed.
Zerachiel: Everyone lent me a hand.

Zerachiel: We absolutely need to get
Effy to break the curse, or else we'll
be in trouble.
Mel: Yes, let's believe in Lady Effy.

Mel: Then, please come to the castle
again tomorrow morning.

Mel: I've already reserved our usual
inn, so today we can relax and take it
easy.

Zerachiel: Understood! I'll take a break
today.
Zerachiel headed towards the inn like this.
It seems like CL was exhausted.

After finishing dinner and taking a
shower...

Zerachiel fell into a deep sleep in the
bed...

Knight: So you are an acquaintance of
Lady Unie? Please make yourself at home.
PushGab 4 ユニエ、偉い人みたいだね

Knight: It seems that Lady Unie and Lord
Ishvald were mercenaries.

Knight: It seems they have known each
other since they were young.
PushGab 2 へぇ、何かありそうだね
